"The package database is locked by another process.\n"
"If no other package manager is running, remove the lock with 'sudo rm /var/"
"lib/pacman/db.lck'."
msgstr ""
"Pakkagagnagrunnurinn er læstur með öðru ferli.\n"
"Ef enginn annar pakkastjóri er í gangi skaltu fjarlægja lásinn með 'sudo rm /"
"var/lib/pacman/db.lck'."

#
